{
  "stem": "10496.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Somebody-- I can't have the Jews to mess up-- mess up my--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right-- 1938, right after-- after November 10, 1938.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, November 10.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they stayed there for about three months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he told me, though, that there were-- not only-- there were Jews, but there were others as well.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Dissenters, communists, or anyone who didn't like Hitler's way of governing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Absolutely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, after-- when he came back from Dachau, he realized that Hitler meant business.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other words, no one was safe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, no one, Jews or gypsy or dissenters, communist, whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] so the die was cast.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My mother left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She went through Sweden.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In other words, she-- I-- I guess she took the train to-- to the north of Germany, and then across to Sweden.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I definitely-- I was crying and she was crying.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was just a-- a-- a traumatic experience.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Traumatic.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it had to happen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'll tell you the truth, it was a good thing it did happen because later on, eventually-- as we were-- we were in southern France, she was able to-- to keep in touch with us all the time, and HIAS also helped a great deal.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "HIAS, H-I-A-S, Hebrew Immigration, something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They-- they were very active in--in trying to save Jew-- Jewish people, and--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "New York.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When she got to New York, she decided to get away-- to-- to go to Boston because, I-- I guess-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't really-- I really don't know exactly why.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She just said-- she just decided to go to Boston, and that's where she found a job as a domestic.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't understand that question.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh,we were alone.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so what happened is that once-- once he came back, he had nothing to do but work for the government.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In other words, the state.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the state had plenty of things for him to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I understand he got very little pay for it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But what is he going to do with me?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he decided to-- he sent me to Heidelberg to foster parents.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They became my foster parents.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were called Wierheimers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Their name was Weirheimer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, by the way, they never made it after the-- in other words, they-- they just never made it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They ended up in, I guess, in Auschwitz or Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How did your father get in contact with these foster parents?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he would-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] he would contact them probably through-- through the phone.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, they had phones already in those days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and that's all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, he-- he visited me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Visited me several times, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In other words, on occasions.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what's he going to do with me?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In other words, he-- he's doing some heavy labor, constructing highways or whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and-- and what's he going to do with me?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There's no school.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So they found someone, a family in Heidelberg, that are willing to--to take me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But my-- my-- my experience in Heidelberg wasn't very pleasant because they already have a lot of these Nazi-- Hitler youths around.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when we used to go to the mountains, you know, you cross the river and went to the mountains, there are always some people that--that would know-- recognize us, and would chase us.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I've learned how to run very, very well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's the only way I can get out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then in-- right in the main street, in the main street, they-- they were able to corner me, and were going to put-- get me into a garage and were going to beat me up.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But for some reason, I just got away from them and ran right down the street, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- but that's the type of situation that I-- I faced.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did you have any identifying markers as a Jew at that point?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, let's see.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In 1930-- about one year.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we-- we corresponded by letters and by him visiting me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, definitely.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He heard from-- and my mother, of course, was very concerned about what was going on in Germany.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she kept-- she kept sending us money and-- and so on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, in other words-- and by the way, the-- the important thing is that that money really came.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In other words, it-- there were middle-- middle men there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it made no difference, and it got there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Got to us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, several times.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Physical-- by physical, you mean--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I saw him, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
